# This file ensures the assets directory is tracked by git.
# 
# To generate PNG diagrams from the Mermaid sources:
#
# 1. Install Mermaid CLI:
#    npm install -g @mermaid-js/mermaid-cli
#
# 2. Generate PNGs:
#    mmdc -i docs/mermaid-diagram.md -o assets/architecture-diagram.png
#
# Alternatively, GitHub automatically renders Mermaid diagrams in Markdown.

